text: The French Congo worm lizard (Cynisca bifrontalis) is a worm lizard species in the family Amphisbaenidae. It is endemic to Gabon. ==References== Category:Cynisca (lizard) Category:Reptiles described in 1906 Category:Taxa named by George Albert Boulenger Category:Endemic fauna of Gabon Category:Reptiles of Gabon
title: French Congo worm lizard
